doctype html
html
    head
        title URL Shortener Microservice
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/main.css')
    body
        h1 FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: URL Shortener Microservice
        quote
            p User stories:
            ul
                li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
                li If I pass an invalid URL that doesn't follow the valid http://www.example.com format, the JSON response will contain an error instead.
                li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

        h3 Example creation usage:
        code
            p #{appUrl}/new/http://google.co.th
        h3 Example creation output
        code
            p {"original_url":"http://google.co.th","short_url":"#{appUrl}/B1Js5gn0"}
        h3 Usage:
        code
            p #{appUrl}/B1Js5gn0
        h3 Will redirect to:
        code
            p http://google.co.th/

        p Created by
        div(class="github-card" data-github="Ceece" data-width="400" data-height="150" data-theme="default")

        script(src="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/github-cards/latest/widget.js")